    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TimGarrisonMN/status/2034325830856290409",
      "reply_text": "Yeah Finch has been improving his game management. Randle's been unstoppable lately",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T20:32:46.565930+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Brian_McInnis/status/2034338478419525938",
      "reply_text": "Pre-tournament practice is key to getting those kinks out",
